      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> lamb skewers</strong> to a baking tray (use<strong> tin foil </strong>to avoid mess!)</p><p>Press the lamb to flatten it slightly and drizzle over the <strong>marinade </strong>(reserve the bowl!)</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? You may need to do this in 2 batches!</p>",
