    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong> and <strong>sliced tomato </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> pepper </strong>and top with the <strong>Kambing-style lamb skewers</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> satay sauce </strong>and<strong> basmati</strong> <strong>rice </strong>to the side and garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
